{
  "description": "A nighttime long exposure photograph captures a vibrant cityscape illuminated by fireworks. A long bridge stretches across dark water, connecting the foreground to the urban skyline in the distance. The city is densely packed with buildings, their lights creating a warm, orange glow that contrasts with the cool blues and blacks of the night sky and water. Above the city, fireworks explode in a spectacular display of red, green, and white bursts. The bridge is lit with rows of white lights. The composition emphasizes the scale of the city and the dynamic energy of the fireworks.",
